'''Esther Mbabazi''' ni umupiloti w’indege z’ubucuruzi wabigize umwuga mu [[Rwanda]], igihugu [[Umuryango w’Ibihugu by’Iburasirazuba bw’Afurika|kigize Umuryango w’Afurika y'Iburasirazuba]] . Niwe mutegarugori wa mbere mu [[Rwanda]] wemejwe ko ari umupiloti w'indege. Yerekeza mu RwandAir, kompanyi y'indege y'igihugu cy'u [[Rwanda]]. <ref name="TheG">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/mar/15/rwanda-first-female-pilot</ref> <ref name="TheC">http://www.cnn.com/2014/06/17/world/africa/rwandas-first-female-pilot-esther-mbabazi/</ref> <ref name="TheK">http://www.konnectafrica.net/esther-mbabazi/</ref>

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Yavukiye mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]] ahagana mu 1988, ku babyeyi [[Rwanda|b'Abanyarwanda]]. Se na nyina ni abapasitori b'ububyutse. Igihe Esther yari afite imyaka igera ku munani, ise yapfuye azize impanuka y'indege  muri [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo]] <ref>https://www.one.org/africa/blog/meet-esther-the-first-female-commercial-pilot-in-rwanda/</ref>. Uyu muryango wasubiye mu [[Rwanda]] mu 1996. Yitoje mu Ishuri Rikuru ry’indege za gisivili muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba muri [[Uganda]][[Ubugande|,]] mbere yuko RwandAir imutera inkunga yo gukomeza imyitozo i Miami, muri Floride . <ref name="TheG" /><ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/77614</ref>  

== Umwuga ==
Esther Mbabazi arangije amasomo ye muri [[Amerika]], yahawe akazi na RwandAir kugira ngo ajye atwara  Boeing 737 na kuri CRJ900, guhera mu 2012, ubwo yari afite imyaka 24<ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/pilote-esther-mbabazi-n-umucuranzi-wa-beauty-for-ashes-bakoreye-ubukwe-ku</ref><ref>https://www.cnbcafrica.com/2019/rwandas-first-female-pilot-esther-mbabazi-reflects-on-her-experience-in-the-cockpit/</ref>.   

